text: Well, then, can I ask you to go get changed now?

Oh, right, today's just a fitting, isn't it?
I wish I could wear it longer!

Haha, yeah.
Let's work hard so you can wear plenty more.

I'll do my best to bring you
more work too.

Right! Thanks!
I'll do my best!

Oh, but before i change,
can I ask for one thing?

Since it's a special day wearing the new outfit...
can you take a photo? Is that okay?

Of course!
Don't hesitate to ask for something like that.
Then please take it with my phone!
